        "content": "<p>I've been reading up on the datatype Timing, and I was unsure how to say \"Take X exactly once, I don't care when\" (<a href=\"http://hl7-fhir.github.io/datatypes-examples.html#Timing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7-fhir.github.io/datatypes-examples.html#Timing\">http://hl7-fhir.github.io/datatypes-examples.html#Timing</a>). Examples include the morning after pill, or certain vaccines. I came up with:</p>\n<p>&lt;schedule&gt;<br>\n   &lt;repeat&gt;<br>\n     &lt;count value=\"1\" /&gt;<br>\n   &lt;/repeat&gt;<br>\n&lt;/schedule&gt;</p>",
        "id": 153837333,
